<subSubSection id="12C0657E1A31FFF1FF4DF8CE867AF83B" pageId="4" pageNumber="288" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="5A6536F51A31FFF1FF4DF8CE867AF83B" blockId="4.[151,1437,810,2025]" pageId="4" pageNumber="288">
<emphasis id="68AEEAE71A31FFF1FF4DF8CE8653F8AF" bold="true" box="[199,317,1891,1917]" pageId="4" pageNumber="288">Remarks:</emphasis>
The new species has been reported from the southern region of Kashmir and during the field surveys, it was observed that 
<taxonomicName id="9DDA4D761A31FFF1FEF4F82A85E1F873" authority="Shah &amp; Usmani, 2022" authorityName="Shah &amp; Usmani" authorityYear="2022" box="[382,655,1927,1953]" class="Insecta" family="Tettigoniidae" genus="Euconocephalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="288" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="farooqi" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="68AEEAE71A31FFF1FEF4F82A85E1F873" box="[382,655,1927,1953]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="288">Euconocephalus farooqi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="68AEEAE71A31FFF1FD1DF82A859FF873" bold="true" box="[663,753,1927,1953]" pageId="4" pageNumber="288">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="739D579C1A31FFF1FD1DF82A859FF873" box="[663,753,1927,1953]" pageId="4" pageNumber="288" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
fed exclusively in the cultivated agricultural field habitats in the planer region of Kashmir valley. These areas were dominated by tall grasses, meadow grass, bushes, and other vegetation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
